(7, 95, 1, 'BBK Live 2019', 62, 'https://www.ticketmaster.es/artist/bilbao-bbk-festival-entrades/912290', 'https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d2905.625409695512!2d-2.963928134514982!3d43.25927192913678!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0xd4e504e9157e4b1%3A0x4419d438dbe4294c!2sBilbao+BBK+Live!5e0!3m2!1ses!2ses!4v1558369089610!5m2!1ses!2ses', 'Bilbao', '2011-07-19 00:00:00', '2013-07-19 00:00:00', '11, 12, 13 Juliol', 'Després de celebrar la seva primera dècada de vida, el festival Bilbao BBK Live segueix sent un dels esdeveniments musicals de referència a tot el nord peninsular. Està especialitzat en música pop i rock però també ha sigut possible escoltar a grups ‘indie’ així com presenciar espectacles de música electrònica. L’èxit ha acompanyat al festival des de la seva primera edició, en la qual va batre les expectatives més optimistes amb més de 50.000 assistents.', '../images/img_2.jpg', '../images/img_201.jpg', 'After celebrating its first decade of life, the Bilbao BBK Live festival is still one of the reference musical events throughout the peninsular north. He specializes in pop and rock music but it has also been possible to listen to ''indie'' groups as well as watch electronic music shows. Success has accompanied the festival since its first edition, which hit the most optimistic expectations with more than 50,000 attendees.', '11, 12, 13 July'),
(8, 96, 2, 'X-Men: Fénix Oscura', 8, 'https://www.ocinegavarres.es/index.php?option=com_cines&task=peli&iid=2683', 'https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d3005.1474055212175!2d1.1986673154178544!3d41.13130797928851!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x12a3fd2a88381393%3A0xf4a593944a004e14!2sOcine+Les+Gavarres!5e0!3m2!1sca!2ses!4v1558390500138!5m2!1sca!2ses', 'Les Gavarres', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '07 Juny', 'En X-MEN: FÉNIX OSCURA, els X-Men s''enfronten al seu enemic més formidable i poderós: un dels seus membres, Jean Grey. Durant una missió de rescat en l'' espai, Jean gairebé mor en ser presa per una misteriosa força còsmica.', '../images/img_11.jpg\r\n', '../images/img_1101.jpg\r\n', 'In X-MEN: FASHION OSCURA, the X-Men face their most formidable and powerful enemy: one of their members, Jean Gray. During a mission of rescue in space, Jean almost dies when taken by a mysterious cosmic force.', '07 June'),
(9, 93, 5, 'The Meet Vincent Van Gogh', 9, 'https://www.ticketea.com/entradas-meet-vincent-van-gogh-experience-barcelona/', 'https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m14!1m8!1m3!1d11975.539113672265!2d2.187815!3d41.376588!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x0%3A0x26e32bda788a411d!2sMeet+Vincent+van+Gogh+bcn!5e0!3m2!1ses!2sus!4v1558369003079!5m2!1ses!2sus', 'Barcelona', '2002-05-19 00:00:00', '2005-06-19 00:00:00', '02 Maig al 05 Juny', 'The Meet Vincent Van Gogh Experience, la primera exposición oficial creada por los expertos del Museo Van Gogh, llega a Barcelona del 14 de marzo al 02 de junio de 2019. Asiste al estreno europeo de una experiencia contemporánea y totalmente interactiva, que tiene como objetivo dar a conocer la vida y obra del artista. Esta experiencia temporal, pensada para toda la familia, no exhibe las obras originales del artista, pues son demasiado frágiles para su traslado.', '../images/img_3.jpg', '../images/img_301.jpg', 'The Meet Vincent Van Gogh Experience, the first official exhibition created by the experts of the Van Gogh Museum, arrives in Barcelona from March 14 to June 2, 2019. It attends the European premiere of a contemporary and fully interactive experience, which aims to make known the life and work of the artist. This temporary experience, designed for the whole family, does not exhibit the artist''s original works, as they are too fragile for his transfer.', '02 May to 05 June'),
(10, 94, 7, 'Applause 2019', 713, 'https://www.eventbrite.es/e/applause-2019-app-marketing-mobile-growth-congress-tickets-53178587587?a', 'https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d2994.2599348159365!2d2.1879647154252093!3d41.36843697926587!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x12a4a3b185625025%3A0x59e80c780f7e2f0b!2sW+Barcelona!5e0!3m2!1sca!2ses!4v1558442817072!5m2!1sca!2ses', 'Barcelona', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '7 Juny', 'Els aplaudiments són una jornada dedicada als professionals europeus de màrqueting i creixement d''aplicacions organitzada per TheTool, PickASO i AppsFlyer, celebrada a Barcelona el 7 de juny a W Hotel.', '../images/img_21.jpg', '../images/img_2101.jpg', 'Applause is one-day conference for European App Marketing & Mobile Growth professionals organized by TheTool, PickASO and AppsFlyer, held in Barcelona on June 7 at W Hotel.', '7 June'),
(11, 93, 1, 'Primavera Sound', 215, 'https://www.primaverasound.es/entradas?_ga=2.110353472.459112582.1558357838-95763229.1558357838', 'https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d11970.510666886998!2d2.1970911357245635!3d41.40389166820058!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x12a4a3589b1ac4d5%3A0x35bd2f24e58a22b2!2sPrimavera+Sound!5e0!3m2!1ses!2ses!4v1558369151093!5m2!1ses!2ses', 'Barcelona', '2029-05-19 17:00:00', '2002-06-19 06:00:00', '29 Maig al 2 Juny', 'Festival internacional Primavera Sound', '../images/img_7.jpg', '../images/img_701.jpg', 'International Music Festival Primavera Sound', '29 May to 2 June'),
(12, 94, 2, 'UNITE With Tomorrowland', 60, 'https://www.eventbrite.es/e/entradas-unite-with-tomorrowland-barcelona-2019-58783884180', 'https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d2990.2495296995357!2d2.1958121154279264!3d41.45550297925786!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x12a4bcf6b4ffe201%3A0x6e7ce799b8284e33!2sTomorrowland+UNITE+Spain!5e0!3m2!1ses!2ses!4v1558369215071!5m2!1ses!2ses', 'Barcelona', '2027-07-19 15:00:00', '2028-05-19 03:00:00', '27 i 28 Juliol', 'El 27 de Julio se celebrará la 3a edición del festival UNITE with Tomorrowland en nuestro país. El Parc de Can Zam, en Santa Coloma de Gramenet, acogerá de nuevo este evento único que se consolida como festival de referencia para los fans de la música electrónica y que ha congregado desde 2017 a más de 45.000 personas.', '../images/img_8.jpg', '../images/img_801.jpg', 'On July 27th will be held the 3rd edition of the UNITE with Tomorrowland festival in our country. The Can Zam Park in Santa Coloma de Gramenet will once again host this unique event that is consolidated as a reference festival for electronic music fans and has brought together more than 45,000 people from 2017.', '27 & 28 July'),
(13, 95, 3, 'Quántica en el CCCB', 0, NULL, 'https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d2993.5534360372612!2d2.164586315755116!3d41.383785979264594!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x12a4a2f4f8b4c02d%3A0xd6c1de3f0a857874!2sCCCB+Centre+de+Cultura+Contempor%C3%A0nia+de+Barcelona!5e0!3m2!1sca!2ses!4v1558392466374!5m2!1sca!2ses', 'Barcelona', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'Fins 24 Setembre', 'L''Art sempre ha estat lligat a lleis universals, còsmiques, des de la proporció àuria a la intuïció de Gaudí. Són relacions que sovint se''ns escapen, perquè ningú té la fórmula de la bellesa, però em sembla fascinant connectar-lo amb la física quàntica.', '../images/img_16.jpg', '../images/img_1601.jpg', 'Art has always been linked to universal, cosmic laws, from the golden ratio to the intuition of Gaudí. These are relationships that often escape us, because nobody has the formula of beauty, but I find it fascinating to connect it with quantum physics.', 'Until September 24'),
(14, 96, 2, 'Spider-Man: Lejos de casa', 8, 'https://www.ocinegavarres.es/index.php?option=com_cines&task=peli&iid=2675', 'https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d3005.1474055212175!2d1.1986673154178544!3d41.13130797928851!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x12a3fd2a88381393%3A0xf4a593944a004e14!2sOcine+Les+Gavarres!5e0!3m2!1sca!2ses!4v1558390500138!5m2!1sca!2ses', 'Les Gavarres', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '05 Juliol', 'Peter Parker torna a SPIDER-MAN: LEJOS DE CASA, ¡la seqüela de SPIDER-MAN: HOMECOMING! El nostre Superheroi amic i veí decideix unir-se als seus millors amics Ned, MJ i la resta de la colla en unes vacances per Europa.', '../images/img_12.jpg', '../images/img_1201.jpg', 'Peter Parker returns to SPIDER-MAN: LEJOS DE CASA, the sequel to SPIDER-MAN: HOMECOMING! Our superhero friend and neighbor decides to join their best friends Ned, MJ and the rest of the group on a holiday in Europe.', '05 July'),
(15, 94, 1, 'Twenty One Pilots Bandito Tour', 50, 'http://www.twentyonepilots.com/', 'https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d2905.974020782439!2d-2.928865184515225!3d43.251966279137044!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0xd4e4e31fb45dfff%3A0x358721cd366788a1!2sPalacio+de+Deportes+Bilbao+Miribilla!5e0!3m2!1ses!2ses!4v1558368694524!5m2!1ses!2ses', 'Bilbao', '2005-07-19 22:00:00', '2006-07-19 00:00:00', '5 Juliol', 'Tanto el perfil de la banda como el de sus integrantes Tyler Joseph y Josh Dun quedaron en absoluto silencio desde julio de 2017, días después de finalizar su sexta gira de conciertos bautizada como Tour De Columbus. Rumores sobre el retorno del dúo estadounidense a la escena musical comenzaron a surgir en abril de 2018 pero no fue hasta julio de ese mismo año que el retorno se llevó a cabo.', '../images/img_4.jpg', '../images/img_401.jpg', 'Both the profile of the band and that of their members Tyler Joseph and Josh Dun remained silent since July 2017, days after completing their sixth concert tour named "Tour de Columbus." Rumors about the return of the American duo to the music scene began to appear in April 2018 but it was not until July of that same year that the return was made.', '5 July'),
(16, 93, 3, 'Lujo. De los Asirios a Alejandro Magno', 0, NULL, 'https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d2994.1278019572032!2d2.147386315425293!3d41.37130797926554!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x12a4a277563a5425%3A0x8d041ff3aaae5e21!2sCaixaForum+Barcelona!5e0!3m2!1sca!2ses!4v1558392289808!5m2!1sca!2ses', 'Barcelona', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'Fins 11 Agost', 'El títol defineix perfectament el contingut de l''Exposició ... perquè aquesta no arriba més enllà. Sorprèn que en remuntar-nos a l''origen de la civilització i la cultura tot quedi en un inventari de joies i ivoris, sense aprofundir -un poquito- en el fascinant i misteriós corredor del món antic', '../images/img_15.jpg', '../images/img_1501.jpg', 'The title perfectly defines the content of the Exhibition ... because it does not go further. It''s amazing that when we go back to the origin of civilization and culture, everything remains in an inventory of jewels and ivories, without deepening-a little bit-in the fascinating and mysterious corridor of the ancient world', 'Until 11 August'),
(17, 95, 4, 'Wanderlust 108 Madrid 2019', 35, 'https://www.eventbrite.com/e/entradas-wanderlust-108-madrid-2019-59246425654?aff=ehomecard', 'https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d3035.3057476630847!2d-3.760140684602504!3d40.46850047935922!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0xd41876927a1dcbb%3A0x1b0da486640c5130!2sHip%C3%B3dromo+de+la+Zarzuela!5e0!3m2!1sca!2ses!4v1558437497533!5m2!1sca!2ses', 'Madrid', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '5 Octubre', 'L''únic "Triatló Conscient" del món.\r\nSé part de la comunidada Wanderlust gaudint de les teves tres activitats preferides -running, ioga, meditació- en una jornada inoblidable.', '../images/img_17.jpg', '../images/img_1701.jpg', 'The only "Conscious Triathlon" in the world.\r\nBe part of the community Wanderlust enjoying your three favorite activities -running, yoga, meditation- in an unforgettable day.', '5 October'),
